#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:102
msgid "Sun Lamp"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:104
msgid ""
"Sun lamps emit light in a given direction. Their position is not taken "
"into account; they are always located outside of the scene, infinitely "
"far away, and will not result in any distance falloff."
msgstr ""
"Les lumières *Sun* (soleil) émettent de la lumière dans une direction "
"donnée. Leurs positions ne sont pas prises en compte ; elles sont "
"toujours localisées en dehors de la scène, infiniment loin, et ne "
"présenteront pas de baisse liée à la distance."

#: ../../manual/render/cycles/lamps.rst:108
msgid ""
"Because they are not located inside the scene, their strength uses "
"different units, and should typically be set to lower values than other "
"lights."
msgstr ""

